---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Shelly Xiong"
  description="Shelly Xiong is a NYC birder on a Linnaean Society committee. Art, writing, and software for the city's birds."
>
  <main style="padding-top: var(--nav-height);">
    <section class="section about" id="about">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">About</h2>
        <div class="about-grid">
          <div class="about-text">
            <p>I'm Shelly. I watch birds in New York City.</p>
            <p>New York gets more migratory bird traffic than almost anywhere on the East Coast. Central Park alone sees over 270 species in a given year. I keep a public eBird profile and write about what I find across the five boroughs.</p>
            <p>I'm on a committee of the <strong><a href="https://www.linnaeannewyork.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Linnaean Society of New York</a></strong>, which has been around since 1878. I also volunteer with a few NYC birding organizations. A few of my photos have shown up in Linnaean field trip reports.</p>
            <p>The rest of the time I work in software (currently as a Website Administrator at the <a href="https://www.metmuseum.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Metropolitan Museum of Art</a>; <a href="/work">full work history</a>). I draw a lot and I'm teaching myself risograph printing. Online I've been <strong><a href="/#contact">@shellylynnx</a></strong> for as long as I can remember, and I publish longer birding pieces as the <strong><a href="/notes/subway-birder">NYC Subway Birder</a></strong>.</p>
            <h2 class="section-title about-connect-title">Connect</h2>
            <p class="section-dek contact-intro">Interested in collaborating or just want to say hello? Email <a href="mailto:subwaybirder@gmail.com">subwaybirder@gmail.com</a> about press, commissions, partnerships, or anything else.</p>
